Nested Loop Join (materializing on the left, streaming on the right) A simple, dependable join.

See Join.nestedLoopLeftJoinBasic(org.apache.jena.sparql.engine.QueryIterator, org.apache.jena.sparql.engine.QueryIterator, org.apache.jena.sparql.expr.ExprList, org.apache.jena.sparql.engine.ExecutionContext) for a very simple implementation for testing purposes only.
